Blitz half the @blueberries{1.5%cups}, @banana{1}, @milk{3/4%cup}, @egg{1}, and @whole wheat flour{1.75%cups} with @baking powder{2%tsp} and @salt{1/4%tsp} in a #blender{}. Fold in remaining blueberries.

Place oil in heated #pan{}, then pour batter to make pancakes. Top with @yogurt (optional){}, @cinnamon (optional){}, @nuts (optional){}, and @honey (optional){}.
